reviews.text:
As a young lawyer I did a lot of PI cases, so I have some insight on Jean Simon Serrano expertise and performance.  Why did I hire Jean?  I firmly believe that whoever represents themselves has a fool for a client.  Shortly after the accident the insurance adjuster called with a laughable offer: “In matter like these we offer $1,000, but in order to expedite this settlement I am offering you $2,000 to settle today.”  Well, it was all I could do to remain professional and not break out into laughter.  Due to Jean’s expertise he settled this matter for $51,000.  Notwithstanding that excellent result that is not why I recommend Jean without any reservation whatsoever.
Jean did the following at all times.
•	Demonstrated expertise and knowledge of the processes and what we needed to do next;
•	Promptly responded to all my questions in a comprehensive manner;
•	Kept me up to date on where we were;
•	Was polite and courteous in all our correspondence;
•	Was professional in all regards.
